<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Password Reset - ShopieApp</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #5e001f; }
        .content { padding: 20px 0; }
        .token-box { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border: 1px dashed #ccc; margin: 20px 0; font-family: monospace; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ShopieApp</h1>
            <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>You requested a password reset for your ShopieApp account. Please use the following reset token:</p>
            
            <div class="token-box">
                <%= token %>
            </div>
            
            <p>Go to <a href="http://localhost:4200/reset-password">our password reset page</a> and enter this token to create a new password.</p>
            <p>This token will expire in <%= expiresIn %>.</p>
            <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>For security reasons, this token can only be used once.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 ShopieApp. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>